pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `attributaire` ( `id_attrib` int(15) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `n_pr_attrib` varchar(25) COLLATE latin1_bin NOT NULL, `adr_attrib` varchar(25) COLLATE latin1_bin NOT NULL, `cont_attrib` mediumint(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id_attrib`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1857 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 COLLATE=latin1_bin;

CREATE TABLE `lot` ( `id_lot` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `id_attrib` int(15) NOT NULL, `id_ilot` int(10) NOT NULL, `id_attes` int(15) NOT NULL, `deb_lot` int(10) NOT NULL, `fin_lot` int(10) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id_lot`), KEY `id_ilot` (`id_ilot`), CONSTRAINT `lot_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`id_ilot`) REFERENCES `ilot` (`id_ilot`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1857 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 COLLATE=latin1_bin;

CREATE TABLE `lotissement` ( `id_loti` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `loti` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, `situ` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, `arrete` int(25) NOT NULL, `tf` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, `c_fonc` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id_loti`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=19 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 COLLATE=latin1_bin;

CREATE TABLE `piece` ( `id_piec` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `id_attrib` int(10) NOT NULL, `nat_piec` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, `num_piec` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, `dat_piec` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET latin1 NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id_piec`), KEY `fk_id_attrib` (`id_attrib`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=1857 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1 COLLATE=latin1_bin;
